sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Administrator
    participant UI as Frontend UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Audit as Audit Log
    
    Admin->>UI: Buka halaman login
    UI->>Admin: Tampilkan form login
    Admin->>UI: Masukkan username & password
    UI->>API: Kirim kredensial login
    API->>Auth: Verifikasi kredensial
    Auth->>DB: Cari data user
    DB-->>Auth: Return user data
    Auth->>Auth: Validasi password
    
    alt Kredensial Valid
        Auth-->>API: Kredensial valid
        API->>Auth: Generate token autentikasi
        Auth-->>API: Return token
        API->>Audit: Log login berhasil
        Audit->>DB: Simpan log audit
        API-->>UI: Return token dan data user
        UI->>UI: Simpan token
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan dashboard
    else Kredensial Tidak Valid
        Auth-->>API: Kredensial invalid
        API->>Audit: Log login gagal
        Audit->>DB: Simpan log audit
        API-->>UI: Return error autentikasi
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan pesan error
        Admin->>UI: Masukkan ulang kredensial
    end
